The reason this is not working is probably due to the missing YAML tags in the struct type of `payload`. Essentially, the YAML processor searches for _lower-case_ fields when we do not specify the expected field names in the tags. In the above case, the struct field `Title` is mapped to an expected `title` field in the YAML data. I hope you get the drift of why this is not working. If not, let me know and I can elaborate further. 😄 

